<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka thagau in a zawm ta a,
 Krista Gerep hing chu;
 Sawttak ka na thahtham ta a,
 Mahleh ka nei kittai;
 Pathien ah michuom ka na hii,
 Isu'n ei lak machun;
 Lauhum ah ka tha A hukdawk,
 Gitloh cheng ei ngaidam.

[V2]
 2. Ka neih chengcheng tawh ka zuona,
 Tatna thisan achun;
 Thagau Thiengtho a hung luta,
 Pathien Cha ka hung hii;
 Ka gitloh cheng, A ngaidam tai,
 A thisan ka hetin;
 Chun, Van gamnuom tung ngei ing ka,
 Krista ka gin phawt chun.

[V3]
 3. Mei leh tuilien in ei um vel,
 Mahleh ei dal zolo;
 Khawvel a lopi nate hin,
 Ei subuoi ta puon au;
 Krista Hukdamna ka neih chun,
 Bangmah awtcha puong ka;
 Thiemloh chan ding lau ta puong ka,
 Ka Pa lung A awi tai.</lyrics>
<title>CHRIST THE TRUE VINE</title>
</song>